{"tid":1673761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 我覺得應該搞個集會聲援段校長","createTime":"2019-10-25T00:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T13:08:04.000Z","uid":333051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5870a33eb217f82cea1b7e9f33b51de09272c9d0","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>應該聲援段校長</ins></strong>因為：<br />\n<br />\n1) 我地應該感激任何憑良知公開仗義執言既人（無論佢幾遲覺醒），尤其係當呢啲人受到四方八面既惡意攻擊；<br />\n<br />\n2) 段校長篇聲明其實已經好持平，批評佢既全部都係歪理，我地冇理由對呢啲歪理沉默，我地唔可以俾班權勢惡晒，如果唔係就會愈黎愈少有影響力既人肯公開仗義執言；<br />\n<br />\n3) 我地要團結一切可團結既人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，多謝段校長，加油。</span>"},{"pid":"702212c53a43ca14920601c91932ceb330d112c6","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"407b3849290eb649cc94e190b7075bf18e942ffb","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96b21625deab097a2a51203a5cb3fc2404ac50c8","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef441fc5f473556af84debce7863dedbad931ed6","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:26:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19cc42c842d0cead66657ddabb8cd4cab26239d0","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"632631b7949f66ef76643bcfd884fe41fb1bea44","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T00:40:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"307c60b1e2a8438f548aa7b475954bfc3637ba55","tid":1673761,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}